<h2 id="AboutTitle"><u>About</u></h2>
<br />
<p id="AboutText">Uplift is a web-based chat bot that responds to emotions. The goal of the project is to facilitate a positive environment no matter what your emotion is.</p>
<p id="AboutText">The application changes background colors and produces gifs depending on the emotion to reinforce positive emotions and counter negative emotions.</p>
<p id="AboutText">The project is a creation at DemonHacks 2017 as a result of an exploration into the world of emotional intelligence, bot frameworks and the one goal of creating a positive world.</p>
